+
+config ADAFRUIT_FRUIT_JAM_RP2350_BOOT_GUARD_CDC_DISARM
+	bool "Disarm BOOTSEL recovery guard when CDC connects"
+	default y
+	depends on CDCACM
+	---help---
+		Automatically clear the early BOOTSEL recovery guard when USB CDC/ACM
